[[Translation:en/Manual/Bridges]]
Whenever you encounter an obstacle, building a bridge might be a good solution. You can use them to build your railroad over a competitor's track, to make your [[en/Manual/Road vehicles]]  go over a lake or to accomplish crossing-free, highly optimized [[en/Community/Junctionary/Main Page]].


